Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:36.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:44.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:51.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:01:00.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:05.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:10.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:15.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:22.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号为了埋葬 战争牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而登陆亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强也在那时得知自己的父亲 已遭长嘴硬鳞鱼号杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但强却将哀伤埋藏于内心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再度登上鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:45.90,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#17 强的新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝 你一个人在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看了还不懂吗？ 我在喝茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然待在这艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就请你照规矩来 不然我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都几岁了 我才不要做那种小朋友体操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只对美容体操有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看你身材东凸西凸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要运动也颇为辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看你做了那么多体操 腰怎么还粗得跟什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要动手是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1 2 3 4 5 6…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在甲板上做体操 感觉还蛮舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 因为一直都窝在 狭窄的船舱内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你最近抱怨变少了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 俗话说久居则安嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 每餐还是都吃鱼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是讨厌船在上浮及下潜时 耳朵会不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚也开朗多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 愈来愈像个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要我教你 保证成功的泡妞绝招？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就相信我长年的经验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重点就在于放手一搏的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放手一搏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 凡事都得试了才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恋爱就是要积极、主动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,置之死地而后生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样才能掌握胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在赢得胜利之前 则是要彻底努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你的绝招是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 只要有花 什么样的女人都能泡到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是在这种地方 我上哪找花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不会自己做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己做？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕴含着满腔的爱意 自己亲手制作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾科
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是想问你 要不要加入粉丝俱乐部？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,粉丝俱乐部？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 就是依可丽娜护士的 粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在入会者皆可得到生活照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是会员证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有谁加入了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来她那么受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？要不要加入？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经有娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想如果两边都要 这样不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来教你一句有用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个归那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个归这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你们有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都几岁的人了 还组什么粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正我是不会加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离开亚特兰提斯后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家突然会主动找我们说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因为他们 在意我们的感受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 大人都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都把我当成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是会认真思考某些事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实我…\N找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回轮到强当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了啦 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他这样哪里像大人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想拜托你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为这样 请你让我成为 这艘船的正式成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望能和大家一起 为爸爸报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我是个小孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你无法杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我们之所以会奋战不懈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全是为了成就一个 让你们不用动手杀人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把手弄脏的 光是我们便已足够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想拜托你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我希望能由你 来帮我说服尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没办法答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原因就如同尼莫船长所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想请你帮我一个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说这话是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很诚恳地去拜托过 尼莫船长与艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果他们对你说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们不答应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我无论如何都想成为一名 能独当一面的船员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你们帮我说几句话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你根本搞错对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你是真的那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不该随便就打退堂鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该直接去说服 尼莫与艾丽朵拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这样倚赖别人 难道靠自己办不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然拜托他人也是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 能够独当一面的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会靠自己的力量 来解决自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道靠自己办不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么在这里发呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没…没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找我有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天空好耀眼 却也好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你不想再飞了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真希望能再飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搭着你制作的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会再制作飞机的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从以前就一直有个构想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那一定能帮我再带你飞上天去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强那小子这回又想搞什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他好像又在制作飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在强那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么到处都在谈情说爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我要开门啰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本连站的地方都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那边有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也算吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 你打算什么时候才要吃饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都已经吃完了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 我现在抽不开身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你的饭怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放在食堂吧 我晚点再去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很快就会再带你飞上天的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完成了 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来只要等它干燥就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成了吗 很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们去看看强的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好难喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题还是出在可动装置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来看看你的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战况还好吗？ 看你好像走进死胡同了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有不懂的地方我可以帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩子闹别扭 可是一点都不可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才没有闹别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩子只要 乖乖倚赖大人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为这是大人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我自己可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且我也不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又在硬撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他正值这样的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种情况常会在男生身上出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拼命想从小孩转变为大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要变成大人？\N为什么要变成大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为不那样就无法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么会无法生存下去？\N为什么会无法生存下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为能赢过大人的 就只有大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等你们再长大一点 就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像阿姨一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是指像艾丽朵拉 那种家伙才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 强一直窝在房里不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 所以娜蒂亚的心情 也一直都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的不是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 他还那么年轻 就把工作看得比女生重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以后可有得苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得还有没有剩下什么食物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以为现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那葛兰迪丝也已经睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说那什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要吃饭自己煮不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会 我从没做过饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为姑姑总是会帮我做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饭一般不是都由人送来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你命还真好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别用那种口气说话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是在羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟桑森从小 就得靠自己来张罗一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论是吃的 还是穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道为什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为不那样做 根本就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 要想独当一面 至少要学会怎么喂饱自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些话真不像是我会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搞什么 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然和你的美貌相比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种人造花就跟纸屑没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但还是用这来代替我害羞的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将它献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那朵花是我做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想把这当作…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预演还是试验之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预演？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢…慢着慢着 冷静点 冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们又结伙来骚扰我孙女了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 谁受伤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会亲自帮他看诊 认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看这伤势的确不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么造成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不清楚耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要把那个拿去给强对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为是娜蒂亚特地为他做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才…才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟陷入热恋的情侣 都会希望能尽量黏在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 那些话是谁教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些人老是 教小孩一些有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有时候会找不到你 原来是跑到这里来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在想事情的时候 就会跑到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要待在机械旁边才能静得下心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真像你的作风\N会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 来 你的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我很努力帮你煮的食物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这样啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要全部吃光喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这叫作『成对消灭引擎』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,据说它的运转原理 远远超过十九世纪的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可说是未来科学的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这架引擎现在也不过是 为了杀害人类而存在的动力源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长那么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我听了好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这可能就是所谓的 成人世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒是想早点长大\N强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个小孩根本无法实现梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能在后头拼命追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要成为大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许就能实现梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我要为了 实现自己的梦想而长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请…请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮 是要送我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 颜色合成费了一番工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 这是你做的啰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢 我会拿它来装饰房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有就是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 我可以分一些给尼莫船长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实船长也很喜欢花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 就那么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果你什么都没说 就跑回来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那放手一搏的精神 跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…不喜欢放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许你会说我没骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我还是宁可等到机会破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题果然还是在于 这里的可动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么做才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道靠自己办不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真希望能再飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩子只要 乖乖倚赖大人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩子是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有啦 我有一些事情想请教你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧 你一开始就不该逞强的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题出在这里的可动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看看 真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如改变一下凸轮形状…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯\N这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果搞清楚了自己会什么 以及不会什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也算是长大了\N原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不能飞还是个问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这架飞机 既没有气球也没有羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的飞得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 理论上很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会又是耍人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 这回并不是由我独力完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也想要坐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个时候就让他们独处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就叫作『你浓我浓』吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来 坐上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提升输出功率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的 它会飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 怎么了？\N飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 快飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 加油\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了\N成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀呵\N呀呵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了 成功了 飞起来了 我们飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚你看 飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是个发明天才
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是个了不起的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他已经可以独当一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你办到了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我第一次这么近距离看云
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像能碰到似的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要钻进去看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于明白了\N明白什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前的我…还有以后的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要留在这艘船上继续学习
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是科学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还要了解这个世界 以及怎么当个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我现在只能飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光靠这样是没办法 带你去非洲的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是当我变成一个 能够保护你的大人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时一定会带你到非洲去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.69,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:24:02.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:07.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:12.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:21.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:31.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:40.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:44.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:49.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:58.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.44,0:25:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 『鹦鹉螺』是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.57,0:25:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是一种大型贝类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大型贝类？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前往南极秘密基地的鹦鹉螺号 发现了大型鹦鹉螺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.72,0:25:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这才是真正的『鹦鹉螺』对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.72,0:25:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『鹦鹉螺对鹦鹉螺号』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.19,0:25:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
